 Published 44 mins ago on March 9, 2021 Nigerian fashion brand Patrickslim in collaboration with Musical artist Ric Hassani just unveiled their newest collection tagged You and I.  The brand’s latest offering is a celebration of unhindered love and togetherness. According to Ric Hassani: I want everyone who purchases a piece or more from this collection to experience and relate with these emotions not just through my music but also my fashion. See the full collection below.            Credits     